      "content": "Wait, so you're a bit lower on the priority for him because of his age and what he's wearing? I'm thinking about how his agitation and restlessness might also be a sign of something else. Should we be looking into potential substance use or maybe just anxiety instead of jumping straight to cardiac stuff, given he looks a bit more \"unstable\" than the first guy?",
